item.title: first lesson
item.description: 12:23 Wednesday 03 June 2015 JST Today is my first lesson with TEM in Lazona. Apparently low level so I brought Side by Side. 14:14 Lesson went well I think, but she said 難しい instead of 楽しかった so I hope she enjoyed it!
